
*****************************************************************************************

 SETUP SPHINX

	Please ensure that you already install sphinx for your platform properly!
	example to use Thinking Sphinx's command :
	
	# To create index data for Sphinx using Thinking Sphinx's settings

		rake thinking_sphinx:index 
	
	# To start a Sphinx searchd daemon using Thinking Sphinx's settings

		rake thinking_sphinx:start 
		
